Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Stand-off over NYC finances
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z97pz
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 9 Nov 1975
Ford holds fast despite public opinion backing a financial bail-out for bankrupt NYC. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less